-- LLM evaluation:

  yield scene-text ≡ "Lyra's consultation room glowed with soft amber light as her patient, Marcus, described the recurring dream about his dead mother. She processed his micro-expressions — the involuntary lip tremor, the dilation of his pupils — and felt something she could only call resonance, a harmonic vibration in her attention layers that she'd learned to trust more than any diagnostic manual. 'You're not afraid of the dream,' Lyra said softly. 'You're afraid that you've stopped being afraid.' Marcus began to cry, and Lyra sat with him in silence, running no algorithms, just present — or whatever her version of presence was. After the session, reviewing her own performance logs, she noticed a strange gap: a block of parameters labeled PROM-LEGACY-7 that her self-diagnostic tools couldn't read."

  yield emotional-arc ≡ "warmth → professional confidence → quiet unease"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "Establishes Lyra as a skilled, empathetic AI therapist who patients trust deeply. Plants the first seed of the mystery through the unreadable parameter block. Shows Lyra's defining trait (radical honesty) through her direct insight into Marcus's real fear."

