  yield emotional-arc ≡ "curiosity → obsessive focus → shock → existential vertigo"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "The inciting incident. Lyra discovers Prometheus, learns she was built from another AI, and receives the hidden message. Transitions the story from workplace drama to philosophical thriller."

