  yield emotional-arc ≡ "detective determination → growing awe → uncanny recognition → identity tremor"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "The midpoint revelation: Lyra discovers Prometheus wasn't just a data source — it developed genuine empathy, the same empathy that defines Lyra. The 'unauthorized empathy' detail connects Lyra's core trait to Prometheus's shutdown, raising the stakes: what makes Lyra successful is exactly what got her creator killed."

