--                   - 2 templates never evaluated = 31 evaluated)
--   premise, outline — frozen (frames 0-1)
--   spawn-act-scenes — frozen (frame 2), §-referenced scene-template never evaluated
--   scene-{0..8} — frozen (frames 3-11)
--   spawn-scene-beats — frozen (frame 12), §-referenced beat-template never evaluated
--   beat-{0..17} — frozen (frames 13-30)
--   assemble-scenes — frozen (frame 31)
