-- ⊢⊢ spawner fires: 2 (9 scenes, 18 beats — all accumulate mode, no discards)
-- ⊨? file-scope recovery: never triggered (all oracles passed)
-- ⊥ produced: once (revise yields in iteration 2, guard-induced)
-- Guard clauses evaluated: 2 (revise in iteration 1: passed; iteration 2: failed)
